attributes.OrgName: The People's Own Organic Power (POOP) Project
attributes.BoundText: We are not based in any specific location. Our work advocates for water stewardship and sanitary responsibility, and we lead workshops and creative engagements throughout the five boroughs.
attributes.PrimST: Waste system (e.g. e-waste drop off location)
attributes.PriLandOwn: We work across public and private lands
attributes.Mission: The POOP Projects uses art, theater and education to stimulate creative conversation about sustainable sanitation for the person, planet and world community.
attributes.Knowledge:
Lower East Side Ecology Center
SWIM Coalition
Riverkeeper
attributes.Goals: We look forward to a world where our waste is redeemed and integrated into the larger system, where the act of pooping is normalized, and where every body in the world has access to safe, dignified sanitation.
